Gilmour, 1962
</taxonomicName>
- Antenna not surpassing middle of elytra.............................................. 
<taxonomicName authority="Tavakilian &amp; Santos-Silva, 2019" authorityName="Tavakilian &amp; Santos-Silva" authorityYear="2019" box="[1203,1334,1596,1618]" class="Insecta" family="Noctuidae" genus="Cendiunopsis" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="7" pageNumber="514" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus" status="gen. nov.">
<emphasis box="[1203,1334,1596,1618]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">Cendiunopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1340,1430,1596,1618]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514">
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[1340,1430,1596,1618]" pageId="7" pageNumber="514" rank="genus">gen. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
